Message format

Worldview
includes
	state						{init, moving, idle, doors_open, emergency}
	last_floor					{1, 2, 3, 4}
	dir							{up, down, stop}
	ID 							{_}
	local_orders 				[{1, 2, 3, 4}]
	#%//(destination)//
format
	tuple
<==> {state, LastFloor, LocalOrders, dir, ID}


Hall Order
includes
	floor 						{1, 2, 3, 4}
	dir							{up, down, cab}
	ID 							{_}
format
	tuple
<==> {Floor, dir}